###########
Compression
###########

Voici les syntaces de decompression, suivi de la compression.

TAR
===

::

    # (de)compresser tar
    tar -xvf archive.tar
    tar -cvf archive.tar repertoire

TGZ
===

::

    # (de)compresser tgz
    tar -zxvf archive.tgz 
    #-C <folder> : destination folder
    tar -zcvf archive.tgz repertoire

BZ2
===

::

    # (de)compresser bz
    tar -jxvf archive.tar.bz2 
    tar -jcvf archive.tar.bz2 


XZ
==

::
    # (de)compresser xz
    tar -Jxvf archive.tar.xz 
    tar -Jcvf archive.tar.xz repertoire


7Z
==

::

    # (de)compresser 7z
    7z e archive.7z
    7z a archive.7z repertoire

ZIP
===

    unzip archive.zip
    zip -r archive.zip repertoire

